    "Recurrence and MortalityTumor recurrence has been predicted effectively by ML models.",
    "For example, early progression and recurrence outcomes for patients with parasagittal and parafalcine meningiomas were successfully predicted by SVM and random forest (RF), achieving AUC = 0.91 [36].",
    "SVMs were used to predict survival for glioma, achieving similar or higher AUC in comparison to a team of neuroradiologists [37].",
